<br>
I told him I was there for Faction and DF Belts which got me the reply too bad you are too high for the camp. You don't need faction and judging by your equipment you can buy DF Belts from me when I get them.....Well this guy then starts shouting for more at orc 1. I would normally just leave the camp but I refuse to just let someone come up and tell me to leave a camp that I had been at for 3+ hours.<br>
<br>
